    <div class="lg:gap-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 mt-12 text-slate-500">
      <p>
        We specialize in connecting companies with skilled automation experts who excel 
        in Zapier, Make (Integromat), and Airtable. Our network includes workflow 
        specialists, integration experts, and automation architects ready to transform 
        your business processes.
