      <p>
        From building complex multi-step automations to creating robust data management 
        systems, we help you find professionals who can streamline your operations. Our 
        candidates bring expertise in API integrations, workflow optimization, and 
        business process automation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-4 grid-cols-2 mt-24 gap-3">
      <div>
        <img
          src="/images/zap1.webp"
          alt="Zapier workflow automation"
          class="rounded-2xl drop-shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-6 duration-300 easy-out transition-all"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/www.png"
          alt="Make.com integration platform"
          class="drop-shadow-2xl mt-6 hover:-translate-y-6 duration-300 easy-out transition-all"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <img
          src="/images/air1.webp"
          alt="Airtable database management"
          class="drop-shadow-2x hover:-translate-y-6 duration-300 easy-out transition-all"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/zap2.webp"
          alt="Complex automation workflows"
          class="drop-shadow-2xl mt-6 hover:-translate-y-6 duration-300 easy-out transition-all"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/make2.webp"
          alt="Integration development"
          class="drop-shadow-2xl mt-6 lg:hidden block hover:-translate-y-6 duration-300 easy-out transition-all"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <img
          src="/images/air2.webp"
          alt="Data automation systems"
          class="drop-shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-6 duration-300 easy-out transition-all"
